Title: What's Eating Gilbert Grissom?
Plot: The killer from The Execution of Catherine Willows returns with deadly results. The entire team is engaged in a race against time to stop this sadistic killer from succeeding again. Grissom is additionally distraught by the idea that this killer is smarter than he is.
ParentalRatingReason: Lightbox Provisional Classification. Official NZ Rating To Be Confirmed.
